          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1601375998255-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> sesame</strong> <strong>noodles</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Serve the<strong> miso-butter chicken noodles</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
